The,Sunlight,Foundation,is,a,non,partisan,non,profit,group,that,uses,technology,to,make,the,U,S,government,more,transparent,and,accountable,Influence,Explorer,provides,site,visitors,with,extensive,and,detailed,information,on,campaign,contributions,lobbying,reports,grants,and,more,This,data,is,available,raw,or,in,the,form,of,charts,graphs,and,Top,lists,The,Influence,Explorer,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,this,information,programmatically,using,REST,calls